@node Main "IsoGate - Documentation"

                              'IsoGate' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'IsoGate' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you use gates to help you
move an 'X' shape from its position at the upper left, to the exit,
which is represented by a small box and is located at the lower
right of the game board.

  It may sound simple at first, but as you may guess, there are
some complications: some gates have a limit of travel. Another
complication is that as you move on a game board, one or more gates
can move randomly...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

